            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "To be very Honest This school (St.Denis) Was no less than a home to me. I have spent my 15years in this school Starting from L.Nursery to class 12. We have spent our Quality of life here we had a quality teachers here who not only teaches us the bookish knowledge but also about the fact of the world teaches us about Discipline. I know that we have be troubling a lot to the teachers in this school bit still they were very kind to us. this is the best school in entire Howrah Zone. I will suggest the upcoming Generations if they ever want to take an Admission in this school you can come here without any Hesitation this school is open for all",
